    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "As you can see it can roughly be split into two parts: the strategic design (content of this article) and the tactical design (content of link:../../micro_architecture/backend/tactical_ddd/tactical_ddd.html",
          "position": {
            "start": { "line": 28, "column": 1, "offset": 910 },
            "end": { "line": 28, "column": 207, "offset": 1116 },
            "indent": []
          }
        },
        {
