          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "]",
          "position": {
            "start": { "line": 89, "column": 114, "offset": 6065 },
            "end": { "line": 89, "column": 115, "offset": 6066 },
            "indent": []
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "start": { "line": 88, "column": 1, "offset": 5919 },
        "end": { "line": 89, "column": 115, "offset": 6066 },
        "indent": [1]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "== Relation to component-oriented architecture",
          "position": {
            "start": { "line": 91, "column": 1, "offset": 6068 },
            "end": { "line": 91, "column": 47, "offset": 6114 },
            "indent": []
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "start": { "line": 91, "column": 1, "offset": 6068 },
        "end": { "line": 91, "column": 47, "offset": 6114 },
        "indent": []
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Strategic DDD is not yet widely used within CCA Germany.\nMost of our large-scale projects instead successfully applied a component-oriented architecture on a big domain, by decomposition into subsystems and subcomponents.\nA business component or subsystem in such an architecture could be interpreted as a bounded context.\nIn such an architecture we also addressed different types of subdomains by classification of different business component types:",
          "position": {
            "start": { "line": 93, "column": 1, "offset": 6116 },
            "end": { "line": 96, "column": 129, "offset": 6567 },
            "indent": [1, 1, 1]
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "start": { "line": 93, "column": 1, "offset": 6116 },
        "end": { "line": 96, "column": 129, "offset": 6567 },
        "indent": [1, 1, 1]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "image:a_component_types.png[]",
          "position": {
            "start": { "line": 98, "column": 1, "offset": 6569 },
            "end": { "line": 98, "column": 30, "offset": 6598 },
            "indent": []
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "start": { "line": 98, "column": 1, "offset": 6569 },
        "end": { "line": 98, "column": 30, "offset": 6598 },
        "indent": []
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Depending on the concrete requirements, a different type with differing guidelines was used.",
          "position": {
            "start": { "line": 100, "column": 1, "offset": 6600 },
            "end": { "line": 100, "column": 93, "offset": 6692 },
            "indent": []
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "start": { "line": 100, "column": 1, "offset": 6600 },
        "end": { "line": 100, "column": 93, "offset": 6692 },
        "indent": []
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Comparing both approaches however we can see that the DDD approach is more business value oriented and also does not try to apply the same technical architecture to each bounded context.\nOn the other it does not make sense to allow complete freedom of architecture styles per bounded context in an enterprise due to economic considerations regarding team rotations, knowledge sharing and in general TCO of the technical solutions.\nTherefore, a definition of architecture archetypes makes sense and should be considered.",
          "position": {
            "start": { "line": 102, "column": 1, "offset": 6694 },
            "end": { "line": 104, "column": 89, "offset": 7213 },
            "indent": [1, 1]
          }
        }
      ],
      "position": {
        "start": { "line": 102, "column": 1, "offset": 6694 },
        "end": { "line": 104, "column": 89, "offset": 7213 },
        "indent": [1, 1]
      }
    },
